						               													<description>Anything goes for your team to WIN!&amp;#10;What happens on the court is solved at the table.&amp;#10;Predict and change the results in your favor!&amp;#10;You don't need to know football to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A fun and dynamic game ideal for soccer lovers!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Roll 'n' GOL you are going to simulate a soccer world cup, but living it from the table!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player will have a sheet where he will write down who, according to him, will win the World Cup, how the games will go, the number of goals and fouls, among other things.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The results of the matches will be given with dice rolls and each player will be able, at the cost of points, to use his special abilities to change the result of the matches.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Try to get your teams to the final! But don't forget to make life miserable for your rivals' teams!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of the championship, the player who obtains the most points in his checkbook wins the game, correctly predicting the results of the matches. Points can be earned by using stars, inventing goals or penalties, or even having the game replayed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Components:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     block of sheets&amp;#10;     2 Dice&amp;#10;     1 schematic card&amp;#10;     15 team cards&amp;#10;     rulebook&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Super Estadio second edition includes a large box so you can store all the game's expansions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
